		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really like the idea of extra content downloaded via network. It's not too difficult to make bonus levels for a NES game and this would keep the game alive and fresh. It's a nice way to add to an existing game without being forced to release a &quot;plus&quot; version or a sequel.

		

